@startuml sm_agent_lifecycle
' ============================================================
' Title:     nasim — Agent Lifecycle State Machine
' Boundary:  nasim code agent CLI + HTTP API
' Purpose:   Process FSM showing all agent states and transitions
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   3.0.0
' Source:    docs/audit/nasim-car-improvement-plan.md
' Review:    —
' Note:      Process FSM, not entity lifecycle. SMT rules from sm.md
'            do not apply (documented deviation).
' ============================================================

title nasim — Agent Lifecycle

[*] --> IDLE : Startup

IDLE --> LISTENING : User input received
IDLE --> SERVING : HTTP request received (server mode)
IDLE --> [*] : /quit or EOF

LISTENING --> THINKING : Input parsed

THINKING --> RESPONDING : LLM returns text
THINKING --> TOOL_EXEC : LLM returns tool_calls
THINKING --> COMPACTING : token_count > budget
THINKING --> ROUTING : ModelRouter resolving
THINKING --> ERROR : LLM call fails
THINKING --> SERVING : Response to HTTP client

ROUTING --> THINKING : Model selected

TOOL_EXEC --> THINKING : Tool result appended
TOOL_EXEC --> AWAITING_APPROVAL : safety_mode=ask AND unsafe
TOOL_EXEC --> HOOK_RUNNING : Hook registered
TOOL_EXEC --> ERROR : Tool execution fails

HOOK_RUNNING --> TOOL_EXEC : Hook allows
HOOK_RUNNING --> IDLE : Hook denies

AWAITING_APPROVAL --> TOOL_EXEC : User approves (y)
AWAITING_APPROVAL --> IDLE : User rejects (N)

COMPACTING --> THINKING : Compaction complete

RESPONDING --> IDLE : Response complete

ERROR --> IDLE : Error displayed

SERVING --> THINKING : Request processed
SERVING --> IDLE : Response complete

IDLE --> PLANNING : /plan command
PLANNING --> IDLE : /plan off

@enduml
